rtificate, banking accounts related financial information and as far as Sellers are concerned, Your business name, addresses of headquarters, customer care number, and all branches, as may be necessary and applicable subject to the nature of the transaction and where permitted for diversity and monitoring purposes, We may collect information concerning Your gender. Further, in case of imported Products, We may collect personal identifiable details of the concerned importer in accordance with the provisions of all applicable laws.</li></ol><p>Personal identification and communication information, as indicated above, are hereinafter collectively referred to as “<strong>Personal Data</strong>”.<br>We also use analytical and statistical tools that monitor details of Your visits to Our Platform and the resources that You access, including, but not limited to, traffic data, location data, weblogs and other communication data.</p><ol><li>YOU HEREBY GIVE YOUR FULL, WILFULL AND FREE CONSENT TO KIKA TO COLLECT, USE, PROCESS, TRANSFER AND STORE ALL PERSONAL DATA array(AS DEFINED ABOVE) AND SUCH OTHER INFORMATION THAT ME BE SOUGHT / REQUIRED FROM YOU UNDER ANY OTHER POLICIES OF THE PLATFORM THAT FORM AN INTEGRAL PART OF THE AGREEMENT, SUBJECT TO THE PROVISIONS OF ALL APPLICABLE LAWS AND IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE TERMS OF THE AGREEMENT.</li><li>Why We collect, Use and Store the Personal Data:<ol><li>Collection of Personal Data for propagating business</li></ol></li></ol><p>From time to time, We may request aforementioned Personal Data from You to process Your applications through Our Platform, and to get valuable feedback from Your experience on Our Platform. In addition, We may also use Your Personal Data for other business purposes or in order to help serve You better, such as informing You of new services, or alliances that could help You. Your posting of any such Personal Data is strictly up to You. While You can visit Our Platform without disclosing any Personal Data, however,